		redirect
		resourceCodes

		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

graphql.query:
query ($query:[QueryStatementInput])
{
	oAuthGetClients (query: $query)
	{
		id
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		resourceCodes
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isRevoked
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
